instructions: Put the dinner plate in the center of the table cloth.
Put the salad plate on the dinner plate.
Put the napkin on the salad plate.
Put the wine glass on the top right corner of the table cloth.
Put the water glass to the right of the wine glass.
Put the salad fork to the left of the dinner plate.
Put the dinner fork to the right of the salad fork.
Put the dinner knife to the right of the dinner plate.
Put the soup spoon to the right of the dinner knife.
